# lychee ignore list — links that are valid in production but unresolvable by
# the local/CI link-check.
#
# Markdown alternates: /foo.md is served by Netlify as a 200-rewrite from
# foo.md.gen (see _redirects). The .md.gen files exist in the repo; the /foo.md
# route does not exist as a file, so lychee's local resolution 404s on it even
# though it works live at yard.apexscript.com/foo.md. Verified in production.
/index\.md$
/architecture\.md$
/skills\.md$
/how-it-works\.md$
/game\.md$
